  "text": "[15] [CITATION_1] introduced the basic equations for gas diffusion in the open channels of the firn layer in terms of the gas flux J (z,t) (where z is the depth in the firn layer and t time, equation (1)). From this equation the concentration C (z,t) in the firn layer can be determined.",
